WEBVTT

00:03.046 --> 00:07.065
You have me at a bit of a
disadvantage, Mr. Griffiths.

00:07.066 --> 00:09.868
Oh, I have you at a total
disadvantage, Ms. Vaughan.

00:10.174 --> 00:11.985
Although I daresay that towel

00:11.986 --> 00:15.016
has never been shown
off to better advantage.

00:17.006 --> 00:18.955
What can I do for you?

00:18.956 --> 00:21.945
As a matter of fact,

00:21.946 --> 00:24.085
you can do exactly as I say.

00:24.086 --> 00:26.025
You see, the Firm has
recently discovered

00:26.026 --> 00:29.975
that our Ben has
been working with the FBI.

00:31.076 --> 00:34.915
Your angelic influence, I assume.

00:34.916 --> 00:37.025
And your mother disapproves?

00:37.026 --> 00:39.025
Oh, you know about my mother, do you?

00:39.026 --> 00:42.005
He has been telling
tales out of school, hasn't he?

00:42.006 --> 00:43.965
Did he also happen to
mention that my sister

00:43.966 --> 00:45.875
has escaped Federal custody,

00:45.876 --> 00:47.895
and is now back with
the Family, as well?

00:47.896 --> 00:49.035
All of which is to say

00:49.036 --> 00:52.065
that you're very lucky it's
me here and not her.

00:52.066 --> 00:53.975
She's no fan of yours.

00:53.976 --> 00:55.945
As you can imagine.

00:55.946 --> 00:58.045
- Yes, well, your sister is...
- Ah, ah, ah, ah.

00:58.046 --> 01:01.055
Before you say anything you'll regret,

01:01.056 --> 01:04.915
please remember she is my sister.

01:04.916 --> 01:09.045
And... she's watching.

01:09.046 --> 01:10.965
They all are.

01:10.966 --> 01:15.875
Say "hello" to Mum, Margot, and Ben.

01:15.876 --> 01:19.926
Or "goodbye," depending
on how Benji plays this.

01:23.026 --> 01:26.895
I trust I can rely on
your full cooperation?

01:26.896 --> 01:28.875
I'll do whatever you want.

01:28.876 --> 01:29.906
Of course you will, dear.

01:30.643 --> 01:32.055
Just tell Rhys to let her go.

01:32.056 --> 01:33.885
She'll be fine.

01:33.886 --> 01:35.935
I promise you. I give you my word.

01:35.936 --> 01:38.945
Oh, but that's the problem, my love.

01:38.946 --> 01:41.055
Your word means nothing to me now.

01:41.056 --> 01:44.975
So, Rhys will take her
somewhere safe until we finish the job.

01:44.976 --> 01:45.985
And then?

01:45.986 --> 01:48.544
And then... we'll see, won't we?

01:48.771 --> 01:50.394
Sybil, if anything happens to her...

01:50.395 --> 01:53.956
Now, now, that all depends on you.

